text: Kristina Kliukevičiūtė (born July 10, 1975 in Kaunas) is a Lithuanian rhythmic gymnast. Kliukevičiūtė competed for Lithuania in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. There she was 37th in the qualification round and did not advance to the semifinal. == References == == External links == * * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Lithuania Category:Sportspeople from Kaunas
